{"tid":1079954,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"新志記海鮮飯店 食評","createTime":"2019-03-27T09:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T05:06:34.000Z","uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1d55003f359591d9d42f3aa487b321048f07ff","tid":1079954,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zdrb1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zdrb1b.png&h=6ddd18f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早兩晚決定去試新嘢 所以去咗太子新志記海鮮飯店 <br />\n我地六個人叫咗 <br />\n大班兩味（炒斑塊、蒸頭腩）<br />\n大馬站煲 <br />\n骨髓炆三鮮<br />\n生炒糯米飯<br />\n京都骨<br />\n三個白飯<br />\n送 蕃薯雪耳糖水<br />\n<br />\n炒斑塊 夠穫氣 <br />\n蒸頭腩 夠滑冇過火 <br />\n大馬站煲 足料 好香蝦膏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n京都骨 酸酸甜甜味道幾好<br />\n生炒糯米飯 雖然唔係真生炒 不過有臘味香 夠鑊氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n骨髓炆三鮮 等如膽固醇炆膽固醇 好食就好食 不過十分之唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n糖水 正正常常 不過不失<br />\n<br />\n環境方面 裝修十分殘舊 衛生亦都麻麻 牆上啲污漬 黑色一撻撻 令人反胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n價錢：$1020六個人 <br />\n<br />\n評分：6.5/10<br />\n<br />\n總結：地踎之選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f2693bec5255b8c3270f49fc5a1223b4018245","tid":1079954,"uid":64374,"like":76,"dislike":3,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f916316b095e02c503c602161afade8aaa2ba513","tid":1079954,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"c2f2693bec5255b8c3270f49fc5a1223b4018245","tid":1079954,"uid":64374,"like":76,"dislike":3,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji